  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施的数据流图，核心是从负载均衡器开始，经过Ingress控制器，最后落到Worker节点上。你先帮我起个头？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到你提到了负载均衡器，但它是作为入口还是中间节点？另外，我看到有两个负载均衡器的节点A和B，它们之间是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "A是外部的负载均衡器，接收流量后把数据发给B，B是集群内部的负载均衡器。A到B的边上标注'Envia datos'，表示发送数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Envia datos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把A指向B，标注'Envia datos'。然后B应该指向Ingress控制器，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，B到Ingress控制器的边用'Petició HTTP'，这是HTTP请求的意思。Ingress控制器后面要接etcd集群做数据验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Petició HTTP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Ingress控制器到etcd的边我标注'Valida datos'。etcd后面是不是还要连Redis缓存？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Valida datos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，etcd需要'Consulta datos'查询Redis，然后Redis要'Responde datos'返回给etcd。这是一个往返。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Consulta datos",
        "Responde datos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "往返画好了。那etcd验证完数据后，要返回给Ingress控制器吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，标注'Devuelve datos'。然后Ingress控制器要回'Respuesta HTTP'给B，也就是内部的负载均衡器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Devuelve datos",
        "Respuesta HTTP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Ingress到B的返回画好了。最后B到Worker节点，这个边写什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "写'Datos procesados'，表示处理后的数据最终落到Worker节点执行。这样整个链路就闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Datos procesados"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完成了。我检查一下：外部LB→内部LB→Ingress→etcd↔Redis→etcd→Ingress→内部LB→Worker节点。所有边和标注都对应上了，你看还有要调整的吗？",
